00:13:23.803 --> 00:13:25.095
Aegon the Conqueror would've had

334
00:13:25.096 --> 00:13:26.430
from his time in Old Valyria

335
00:13:26.431 --> 00:13:28.932
as. like. a House
Targaryen family heirloom.

336
00:13:28.933 --> 00:13:30.642
<i>a suit of armor that
