00:13:47.744 --> 00:13:49.329
- Nice armor.
- Yes!

344
00:13:49.996 --> 00:13:52.414
Joanna Lynch: <i>Aegon's armor
was a huge challenge for us.</i>

345
00:13:52.415 --> 00:13:54.124
