361
00:14:38.169 --> 00:14:40.379
<i>So that was 20 weeks of work.</i>

362
00:14:40.380 --> 00:14:42.506
<i>It's got quite
architectural shapes</i>

363
00:14:42.507 --> 00:14:44.967
<i>within the forms and outline.</i>

