00:16:05.548 --> 00:16:07.633
<i>forms and shapes. lift patterns</i>

394
00:16:07.634 --> 00:16:09.885
<i>from the surfaces
of every piece.</i>

395
00:16:09.886 --> 00:16:12.429
<i>create artwork for
the Valyrian steel.</i>

396
00:16:12.430 --> 00:16:14.264
<i>and then apply it
to every surface.</i>

397
00:16:14.265 --> 00:16:16.351
<i>So. it was quite involved.</i>

398
00:16:17.185 --> 00:16:19.187
Speaker: Give it a bit
of a shimmy. I reckon.

399
00:16:20.814 --> 00:16:23.817
- That's it.
